{"tid":2229420,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"胡錫進：感謝美國禁共產黨員移民 令家產及人才留在境內","createTime":"2020-10-04T11:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T06:30:34.000Z","uid":21470,"like":332,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"9e84b5be88e668a9c817e2991bbbad65ad30b343","tid":2229420,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:36:33.000Z","msg":"美國不再受理共產黨員移民申請 胡錫進：並非壞事<br />\n<br />\n美國公民及移民服務局發出新政策文件，今後將不再受理任何國家的共產黨員移民申請，指新政策是美國國會通過&ldquo;應對安全威脅&rdquo;法案的一部分。任何人只要加入過共產黨或極權主義政黨，無論是在哪個國家，或是否仍在黨內，他們移民美國的申請都將被拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n北京環球時報總編輯胡錫進在交網站帖文說，中國有許多優秀人才是共產黨員，美國有關措施，反而打破了不少人的幻想，讓更多人才留在國內，並非壞事，更重要的是，如今非中國共產黨黨員的民眾，對移民美國的興趣也大大降低。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2360146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2360146&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilwy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=b2e3e81d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2360146</a>"},{"pid":"5aa26526f96ebd989da0336fdfb5f614128ec859","tid":2229420,"uid":231583,"like":347,"dislike":2,"score":345,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3585532e3a1cb8fdfc864d211e51bb23613c4598","tid":2229420,"uid":31520,"like":103,"dislike":1,"score":102,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"唔去美國 都唔會留係中國喇 死on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e46bd130a77c6323bf8ffa7fc4560a338c2075","tid":2229420,"uid":55089,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9450a28a6ae8aba71991d2a14a6a09058f47700b","tid":2229420,"uid":59511,"like":26,"dislike":1,"s